      <odd id="aspace_aed7612babd7b723c6d6712533c3f5e3">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-J-2 (YRG 13-J-2), Records of the master of Pierson College.</p>  
      </odd>
